<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <title>JX Clinic</title>
    <style>
        .background {
            background-color: #ededef;
            padding: 115px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        span {
            display: block;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .container-1, .container-2 { 
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container-1 p, .container-2 p { 
           font-weight: bold;
           font-size: 30px;
           padding-top: 120px;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: black;
            color: #fff;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border: none;
            width: 20%;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: black;
            color: #cec9c9;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include ('partials/navbar.ejs') %>

    <div class="background">
        <p class="title">About Us</p>
        <span><b>JX Clinic</b> is dedicated to ensuring that each patient's healthcare journey is holistic,</span> 
        <span>seamless, and cost-effective. This commitment is realized through our in-house services and robust</span>
        <span>partnerships across diverse medical, surgical, and allied health specialties. We remain steadfast in our</span> 
        <span>commitment to patients, ensuring accessibility even during travels abroad via our telehealth services.</span>
    </div>

    <div class="container-1">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <p>Partner With Us</p>
                <span>We continuously seek to forge enduring and purposeful</span>
                <span>partnerships with like-minded individuals who align with our</span>
                <span>shared mission.</span>
                <a href="/contactUs" class="btn btn-primary btn">Partner With Us</a>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src=" https://plus.unsplash.com/premium_photo-1673958771993-f1c596da32f5?q=80&w=2940&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" class="card-img" alt="Patner With Us Image" width="100%">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-2">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src=" https://www.internationalinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Singaporean-doctors-scaled.jpg" class="card-img" alt="Join Us Image" width="100%">
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6">
                <p>Join Us</p>
                <span>Join our team at JX Clinic where we will work with you to</span>
                <span>develop a personalized career plan that is suited to your timeline, skills,</span>
                <span>and aspirations. We only ask that you share our common goal, ensuring</span>
                <span>each patient's healthcare journey is seamlessly managed for them.</span>
                <a href="/contactUs" class="btn btn-primary btn">Join Us</a>
            </div>

           
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include ('partials/footer.ejs') %>
</body>